Extension: VhDir Ehr

Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/vhdir/StructureDefinition/ehr Version: 0.2.0
Active as of 2017-11-13 Computable Name: EHR

Context of Use

This extension may be used on the following element(s):

  • Location

Usage info

Usage:

  • Use this Extension: VhDir Location
  • Examples for this Extension: Founding Fathers Memorial Hospital Heart and Vascular Institute, Founding Fathers Memorial Hospital

Formal Views of Extension Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots, and how the XML and JSON presentations work.
